# **NEW WEAPON SPECIAL RULES**

### **Markerlight**

This weapon does not inflict wounds. Each successful hit places one Markerlight Token on the target unit. Tokens remain on the target unit until the end of the current turn.

### **Networked Munitions (Airbursting Frag Projector)**

This weapon may be fired using Indirect Fire as a Barrage weapon (no line of sight required, scatter 2D6" \+ scatter dice). Alternatively, the firing model may spend one Markerlight Token from the target unit to fire the weapon as Direct Fire using the firer's Ballistic Skill. When fired as Direct Fire in this way, line of sight is drawn from the model that placed the Markerlight Token, not the firer.

### **Networked Marker Relay (Smart Missile System)**

This weapon requires line of sight to fire. However, the firing model may spend one Markerlight Token from the target unit to fire without line of sight. When doing so, line of sight is drawn from the model that placed the Markerlight Token. When a Markerlight Token is spent in this way, the weapon also gains Ignores Cover for that attack.

### **One Use**

This weapon may only be fired once per game. After firing, the weapon is expended and may not be used again for the remainder of the battle. Mark the weapon as expended after use.

